{"tid":693245,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當被問到20萬訟費何時找數時，唐琳玲旋即以猙獰目光斜視記者","createTime":"2018-06-07T10:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T11:28:31.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0f0eb6b82d43f0a01f20ba578db71dc4cc83bce8","tid":693245,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:13:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180606/large/1528295940_7645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180606%2Flarge%2F1528295940_7645.jpg&h=279c6333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">唐琳玲甫聽到20萬元訟費，就會面露不悅之色。</span></div><br />\n<br />\n被控刑事藐視法庭罪成的支那癲婆唐琳玲，目前仍繼續賴在深圳一間桑拿會所內，看似還會住上一、兩天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。不過最惹關注的是，到底她被裁定須支付19.7萬元懲罰性訟費，至今找數未呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？《蘋果》記者多番就此向唐琳玲詢問，但她一直以「我很忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  」或「我不懂你在說甚麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」來迴避答案，甚至甫聽到有關「償還20萬元」等字眼時，她會顯得特別敏感，除裝作繼續看電腦螢幕，垂頭不語外，又或露出猙獰的目光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，用炯炯有神的眼睛斜視記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，甚至立即召來服務員趕驅記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不許記者再走近她<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180606/58286292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180606%2F58286292&d=vGq%2Bnr1PS76k8%2FORFM7KfePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=6e4a7e8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180606%2F58286292&h=1b6baa8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180606/58286292</a>"},{"pid":"84a0529fd3693f3461ddd30509bae11c85e1becd","tid":693245,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bac0aa314525ed332f929add76e09e0667eb274","tid":693245,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:16:01.000Z","msg":"據《蘋果》連日追訪，發現在庭外開籠雀般大騷英語的她，跟現時賴在桑拿會所內的她大相逕庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，今日她選了餐廳中央一張大圓枱，但就只有她獨自佔用該張可容納半圍枱人的餐桌，枱面放有她的手提電腦及大量文件，全日她都幾乎無離開該座位，只間中去打個電話或上廁所，其餘時間她就在看文件，以及不斷上搜尋網，靜靜地細閱有關她的新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180606/large/1528295981_60fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180606%2Flarge%2F1528295981_60fc.jpg&h=d38217ad&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n對於她曾公開聲稱「有多張信用卡，最重要的卡不停的消失」，但記者她連日在會所內消費不少，除昨天叫了白切雞和白飯等，今天午餐她又叫了點心，以及晚餐點了咕嚕肉配白飯，還有滷水拼盤，同樣吃得相當滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，加埋昨天她又沖涼擦背兼揼骨，睡前又要「鬆鬆腳」，粗略估計埋單至少要1千人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180606/large/1528295624_c7ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180606%2Flarge%2F1528295624_c7ef.jpg&h=d24ae506&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"86de1243d6c54f4e27b6a9eb0608db95b6e957f1","tid":693245,"uid":19055,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"On9未找數就放人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18914fc3abd307eda0d2c4d6c8b18c5f147dd8c","tid":693245,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"86de1243d6c54f4e27b6a9eb0608db95b6e957f1","tid":693245,"uid":19055,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"On9未找數就放人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:21:12.000Z","msg":"這就是香港.JPG"},{"pid":"18006f660ff119e6ab0b5ef454306f0d0029bc35","tid":693245,"uid":24759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"個記者會唔會有事㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840e1ac05ddb7dc7444d76c126b95cef57ea7010","tid":693245,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"留名佢連找呢筆數都找唔到"},{"pid":"019c4ac7b5dc23834d1670475248fc673cf709d6","tid":693245,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e18914fc3abd307eda0d2c4d6c8b18c5f147dd8c","tid":693245,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"86de1243d6c54f4e27b6a9eb0608db95b6e957f1","tid":693245,"uid":19055,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"On9未找數就放人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:21:12.000Z","msg":"這就是香港.JPG"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"有身份證都被遣返<br />\n唐琳玲冇居留權冇得揀<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180607/20413763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180607%2F20413763&d=vGq%2Bnr1PS76k8%2FORFM7KfePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=f7424cb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180607%2F20413763&h=2dcf1d2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180607/20413763</a><br />\n<br />\n消息人士解釋唐女遭「遣返」，是因為她持有的並非「香港永久性居民身份證」，故她沒香港永久居留權，據悉今次她是持《商務簽注》來港聽審的，但她在候審及被扣押期間《商務簽注》卻已過期，無權再留港，當局遂經羅湖把她遣返內地。不過「遣返」的嚴重性遠不及「遞解」，故預料唐女日後仍有機會獲准再次來港。<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉雄解釋，現時由內地或外國來香港工作、讀書又或是做外傭，都可能會獲發「香港居民身份證」，但持有這種身份證不代表有香港居留權，一旦持有人犯事或被列為不受歡迎人物，即有被遣返原居地的可能。反過來說，一名香港永久居民持有的「香港永久性居民身份證」的背面則印有字樣，列明「本證持有人擁有香港居留權」字句，所以當局是不能把香港永久居民「遣返」或「遞解」返內地或其他國家。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，唐琳玲疑是持內地公安機關發出的《商務簽注》來港，持《商務簽注》來港，《商務簽注》有效期由三個月至一年不等，持有人可以一次或多次進出香港，但每次入境香港最多只可留港七天。但由於唐女來港聽審期間被檢控及遭扣押多天，故她的《商務簽注》日前已經過期，當局遂於6月4日（她坐滿7天監）後把她遣返內地。"},{"pid":"a6cf6e5e23a769c89745aaaff31af9afbc86d007","tid":693245,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"有無人知佢幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182ac55b387bf7a134dead6a91d72d729061e06a","tid":693245,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:33:34.000Z","msg":"據東網記者取得唐琳玲周三中午的消費收據所見，她當天胃口不錯，除了喝鮮豆漿，還叫了白切雞，另加兩碗白飯，還有紅豆雙皮奶作甜品，僅中午的飲食消費埋單便要181港元。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180606/photo/bkn-20180606200046536-0606_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180607055730\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180606%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180606200046536-0606_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180607055730&h=2d8b46ce&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180606/mobile/bkn-20180606200046536-0606_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180606%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180606200046536-0606_00822_001.html&d=vGq%2Bnr1PS76k8%2FORFM7KfePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=280d6a6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180606/mobile/bkn-20180606200046536-0606_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0a005a54abb21cf868385108bc62725904298a0f","tid":693245,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6cf6e5e23a769c89745aaaff31af9afbc86d007","tid":693245,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"有無人知佢幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},